SUMMARY:LADR Week 1, Day 1: From Concrete to Abstract
DESCRIPTION:Reading: Axler, Sections 1.A & 1.B.\n\nConceptual Focus: Understand the leap from Rⁿ properties to the formal axioms of a vector space (1.19). Why these axioms? They are the essence of "linearity".\n\nTool Integration:\n- ChatGPT: Ask for a simple analogy for a vector space that isn't about arrows (e.g., "Explain a vector space like it's a collection of recipes").\n\nExercises:\n1. 1.A, Ex. 3\n2. 1.A, Ex. 9\n3. 1.B, Ex. 2
